title: Marvel Ultimate Spider-man 1
description: Take the Ultimate Spin as the Hit DisneyXD show swings out of the TV and into your hands! By day, he's Peter Parker, mild-mannered high school student. But by night, he's the Ultimate in super heroics - Spider-Man! And he's just the beginning of a super-hero universe... COLLECTING: MARVEL UNIVERSE ULTIMATE SPIDERMAN 1-4
author: Dan Slott
